    Scope and Contents
Files contian letters, memos, minutes and reports that in the aggregate, provide a detailed view on one year's adminstrative problems and solutions.  Notable is documentation of long- range planning, in which demographic changes and new financial constraints affecting higher education in the 1980s are dramtically apparent.  
  
